      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "人物關係",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "人物",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "簡述",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "岩王帝君",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "岩之魔神。歸終與之交好，定下盟約。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "現在以凡人",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "鍾離",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的身份生活。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2523,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/16/157749474/46ee1323ddfe94fe1707c1d50912504e_6818674551392663484.png",
                      "name": "留雲借風真君",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "和歸終一樣精通機關術的仙人。據說岩王帝君曾評價歸終的機關更優秀。 (*1)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "歌塵浪市真君",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "又名萍姥姥。她曾與歸終爭論機關和作曲的問題。 (*1)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "馬科修斯",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "爐灶之魔神。他是歸終的朋友之一，也常被邀請到她家作客。 (*2)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "現在以香菱取的名字",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "鍋巴",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "生活。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "right",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*註1：來自劇情預告-「餘音縈心」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "right",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*註2：來自「磬弦奏華夜」的活動劇情",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "相關物品",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
